A Separation;;92;;99;;PG-13;;When Nader (Payman Maadi), a bank employee, refuses to leave Tehran, his wife, Simin (Leila Hatami) sues for divorce in the hope that she can make a better life for their young daughter abroad. Needing someone to care for his senile father while he's at work, Nader hires Razieh (Sareh Bayat), a married woman whose chador hides her pregnancy. One day, after becoming angry with Razieh, Nader shoves her, and she has a miscarriage, leading Razieh's husband to take Nader to court.;;Drama;;Asghar Farhadi;;2011;;Peyman Moaadi,Leila Hatami,Sareh Bayat,Shahab Hosseini,Merila Zare'i,Babak Karimi,Shirin Yazdanbakhsh,Sarina Farhadi,Ali-Asghar Shahbazi,Kimia Hosseini;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/a_separation_2011